flagList.name: BOTH_GUID_ABSNT
flagList.description: This bit is set true when both persistent and session GUIDs are absent

flagList.name: MOZILLA_PREFETCH
flagList.description: This bit is set true when there is a Xmoz:prefetch header

flagList.name: SESSION_GUID_ABSNT
flagList.description: This bit is set true when  persistent GUID present and session GUIDs are absent

flagList.name: PERSTNT_GUID_ABSNT
flagList.description: This bit is set true when persistent GUTD absent and session GUIDs are present

flagList.name: NON_USER_REQ
flagList.description: Generic flag for non user initiated request. E.g. ‘Mozilla Prefetch’ , ‘content type mismatch for image ’

flagList.name: ERROR_IN_PROP_OR_DATA
flagList.description: Set when there is an error in property, flag or data

flagList.name: DETECTED_BOT
flagList.description: This request is detected as being from a BOT

flagList.name: CONTENT_TYPE_MISMATCH_FOR_IMAGE
flagList.description: Set when request is image and response is text/html

flagList.name: SAFARI_PREVIEW
flagList.description: Flag to detect that the request was part of Safari Preview (Top Sites) feature

flagList.name: USER_FROM_GEO_COUNTRY
flagList.description: Is user accessing the site from one of the Geo countries list
